a.n: Agent Binky: Pets of the Universe I (24)

p.k: Fly Me To Balloon When Small Human comes home with a robot-shaped balloon tied around his wrist, the team naturally assumes it's a robot.
p.d: Binky is an indoor cat who is a member of a secret agency. Teamed with like-minded pet agents, they are on a mission to keep their humans and "space station" safe from "aliens".
